# Horizon AIOS — User Personal Ignore Layer
#
# Add patterns here for folders or files you want excluded from the root OS
# repo that are personal to you or this machine. This file is version-
# controlled (portable across machines), but its contents are applied via
# .git/info/exclude so they never interfere with system-level .gitignore.
#
# The pre-commit hook keeps .git/info/exclude in sync with this file
# automatically. Changes take effect on the next commit.
#
# Examples:
#   MyPersonalNotesFolder/
#   scratch/
#   *.private

